description:
Naze Youka is a junior of Class 13 and a member of the Flask Plan`s Thirteen Party. Her project name is Black White. She was originally a Special but worked her way up to Abnormal. She is the middle child of the Kurokami siblings, being younger than Kurokami Maguro but older than Kurokami Medaka.
Source: Medaka Box Wikia
name: Naze Youka
